high_descs: Turn around and make a left to face the bread on the counter.
Pick up the clear bowl to the left of the bread on the counter.
Turn around to walk to the fridge.
Chill the bowl in the fridge, removing it again afterwards.
Turn left to walk towards the counter.
Set the bowl on the counter to the right of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Chill a clear bowl in the fridge to put on the kitchen counter.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the counter top to your left.
Pick up the glass bowl to the left of the loaf of bread, on the counter top.
Turn to your right and go to the refrigerator, across the kitchen, to your right.
Place the bowl on the top shelf of the refrigerator, wait a moment for the bowl to chill, then remove the bowl from the refrigerator.
Turn to your left and go to the counter to the right of the sink.
Place the bowl to the right of the plate, on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled bowl on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around and walk forward then turn left to face the counter
Pick up the clear bowl from the counter
Turn around and walk up to the fridge
Put the bowl in the fridge then remove it
Turn left and walk up to the counter right of the sink
Put the bowl down on the counter just right of the plate
anns.task_desc: Put the chilled bowl on the kitchen counter
